Adds the four shared workspace packages the rest of v2 depends on.

* @gv/types (src/index.ts + identity/errors/feature-flags/audit/system-config):
  zod schemas + inferred types for the Phase 0 control_plane surface.
  Canonical ErrorEnvelope matches docs/blueprint/reference/API_SURFACE.md.
* @gv/config (index.ts): AppEnv, ControlPlaneEnv, WebEnv zod parsers that
  refuse to boot if required env keys are missing. DEFAULT_PORTS map for
  the 11 v2 services.
* @gv/api-client (src/client.ts + endpoints/): ApiClient with correlation
  ids, bearer token injection, ErrorEnvelope unwrap into ApiError, and
  endpoint factories for auth, feature-flags, system-config, health.
* @gv/ui (src/components/): cn() util, Button, Badge, Card, EmptyState,
  PageHeader, ToDoBanner (marks stub pages so they can't be mistaken for
  real screens).

All four packages declare composite tsconfigs referencing tsconfig.base.json
and expose 'workspace' export conditions so pnpm symlinks resolve without
a build step.

Phase: 0 / blueprint v3.0.0
PR: 2 of 8 in v2.0.0
